reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful, very well made. easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Love this cabinet, bought for my daughter for her new apartment. Fits perfectly in her bathroom. Lots of storage

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars you get what you pay for, but in a good way!
reviews.reviewText: I'm very happy with this purchase overall, and would buy it again. My thumbnail picture may have some distortion to it on the rattan that doesn't exist in real life, the door and drawers look perfect.Good things: 1) Everything came in absolutely perfect condition, the directions to put it together were very good, all the pieces fit together well, the cabinet looks great and works well 2) Several people in the reviews have commented on the drawers but I'm happy with them and mine don't fall out if you put the stops in as instructed. 3) It's an excellent valueBad things: 1) It took me 2 1/2 hours to put together and I'm a handy guy. I didn't make any mistakes or have to redo anything, it just takes a long time. You have to carefully look at everything or you might make a mistake 2) the cabinet is actually quite a bit smaller than I thought it would be, but the dimensions are accurate so that's on me for not knowing this before I got it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great storage addition. Love it's design.
reviews.reviewText: I received this once before but it had a missing piece and 2 pcs of something else. Easily returned it and received its replacement in less than a week. It's veneer on pressboard so it's not top quality but it's sturdy, thick, aligns nicely and will provide me the storage I need. It was easy to assemble and looks great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and Sturdy
reviews.reviewText: It’s well made and easy to put together. The caning on the drawers and door on black really pops. Definitely recommend this cabinet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 9, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It’s ok-update 6/17/22-GREAT customer service!
reviews.reviewText: Update-Seller saw my review and reached out to me asking what they could do to rectify the situation. I told them nothing, just make sure to update the instructions for future buyer:I got another message that they did that and also refunded me some of the money from my purchase. I cant tell you how nice it is to see fantastic customer service.I will definitely buy from this seller again knowing that if I have an issue they will make it right. 👍So, it’s pretty and looks nice at the end of the day.It came in like 60 pieces, definitely intimidating. The directions…well. At first I was impressed. But then they were wrong and unclear in some parts and that matters SO MUCH.I ended up going right through the pressed board on the top because I pushed too hard. Easy thing to do. Luckily I fixed with some super glue.Some stuff I just didn’t get. I did it but I feel like I worked for 2.5 hours and honestly, it could have been built better. Not super sturdy, drawers fall out due to lack of tracks.In fairness I built a lot of stuff on my own, without my husband. I’m not bad at it; but this was definitely more complicated that I am used to. Regardless, it’s done and pretty, but not super functional. In hindsight I wish I had just spent more and paid more attention to the complication of building it. It won’t last long but serves the job for now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I was looking for!
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been searching for a while for something to store media-type stuff and this is so perfect for the price point. The size, shape, layout are exactly what I was looking for. The finish even coordinates well with my reclaimed wood furniture which I thought would never happen. It does have a boatload of pieces and there are a couple places the instructions could have been a tad clearer but I don’t even care because I’m just so pleased with it. Of course I’d prefer something that is solid wood but I didn’t want to spend the money and honestly this is pretty well put together, even including braces for the back panel. I rarely see that in this kind of furniture. I agree that a screw gun is very helpful in places. The drawers definitely take some getting used to. This isn’t something we will be getting in and out of every day so it’s a non-issue for us. I hope it holds up okay.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Poor Assembly Instructions and door doesn’t fit
reviews.reviewText: The instructions are poorly written. It is difficult to assemble! When i finally assembled everything the door doesn’t fit. It doesn’t stay screwed on because the hole is too big for the screw.. it giant fit even to close. i called Amazon and i was instructed to dismantle and return it for refund! So annoyed. I expect to pay for something and have that item to be at 100% functionally well instead i now have a item that partially serves it purpose. A partial refund should have been offered!!!! I took the door OFF!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A little cheap but nice looking
reviews.reviewText: It holds extra storage just fine. It’s definitely not the best quality but it works!
Cutest entryway cabinet! It is smaller but the perfect size for a small space, instructions were clear, took me approx an hour to put together! Love it!

I have limited space in my foyer and this cabinet has the dimensions I need. All pieces were labeled and set up was easy. The finishing is not the best and drawers (especially the bottom 2) would fall off if you free your hand after opening them. I think that has something to do with the design of the drawers.
